original_title: The String Cheese Incident Live at Red Rocks
overview: SCI’s 25th anniversary tour wouldn’t be complete without a stop at our all-time favorite venue! We’ll be playing three Incidents at Red Rocks Park & Amphitheatre this July, and we’ve called on a few very special guests to join us!  Cory Wong will kick things off on Friday, and on Saturday we’ll team up with our longtime pal Keller Williams to celebrate the 20th anniversary of Keller’s album, “Breathe”, which will be played in its entirety! On Sunday we’ll do some pickin’ with the Del McCoury Band and help Del ring in 80 years of bluegrass royalty.
title: The String Cheese Incident Live at Red Rocks
